    "The main applications of this paper are: the proposed approach provides the solution for the problem present in the power sector, such as to wastage of electrical power due to electricity theft.",
    "This model can efficiently be applied by the utility companies using the real electricity consumption data to identify the electricity thieves and reduce the energy wastage and finally, the proposed approach can be used against the all types of consumers who steal the electricity.",
    "The key contributions of this paper: A comprehensive data preprocessing is performed using interpolation, three sigma rule, and normalization methods to deal with missing values and outliers in the dataset.",
    "The data pre-processing step gives the refined input, which improves the performance of the classifier.",
    "A class balancing technique, K-means SMOOTHE, is proposed to address the problem of imbalance data."
